{"type": "article", "id": 17017, "title": "这家像灯塔一样的餐厅，去马尔代夫不要忘了看看", "description": "其实，里面的酒窖更有吸引力", "date": "2015-11-03T18:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3967, "name": "餐厅"}, {"id": 5729, "name": "度假"}, {"id": 10532, "name": "马尔代夫"}, {"id": 18221, "name": "Petr Kolar"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 104, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607150936n4m0coJVk2jFxBQN.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t马尔代夫的维拉私人岛（Velaa Private Island Maldives）是一个专门度假的岛屿，占地 16 公顷，2013 年 12 月才开始对外开放。岛上只有屈指可数的度假别墅，总计下来共 45 个房间，让过来的人可以安静地享受度假时光。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t维拉岛上最大的标志是 Tavaru 餐厅，由捷克建筑师 Petr Kolar 设计。在混凝土的桶状构造外加了一层浅灰色半透明的幕墙，中间有许多大的镂空孔，像是随风而动。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t不规则的外形正好契合了这座岛的自然野性，与城市里规整的建筑相区别，让人感到放松。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144231zXmZvpG0Bl3VJiK4.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t白天，光线会从这些孔里透进来，相当于是窗户。到了夜晚，餐厅的橙色的光会通过半透明的幕墙透出来，远远看过去就是岛上的灯塔。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607150928vVEaKm9J31bASGWl.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607150929LNbfXBeSh1vGFruM.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071509298QRpt7bDTsBXZwAC.jpg\" title=\"楼梯围着桶装的主体外旋转上升\" alt=\"楼梯围着桶装的主体外旋转上升\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>楼梯围着桶状的主体外墙旋转上升</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t餐厅的一二层完全打通成为大型的酒窖。围着一圈装修了木质的柜子，仿佛置身于洞中，很气派。这里据说收藏了全世界最好的葡萄酒。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607150930MVJHt2YvoUjasbdg.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071509313sQGPJKXRkxZLlHU.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.921875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607150931S4RspGqtwxVeKlgI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607150932c6jpRoN4OLMygfeA.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t楼上是环形餐厅和休息区，提供亚洲各地的美食。因为有 23 米高，最上层可以看到全岛的风景。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607150932KSbNqrB31FIvQeyY.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.59659091\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607150933oxrPUQX1d3vK6hVW.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.59659091\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607150933gqe9LM6IcEnYvlxC.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607150934jwiox10NgqOARnYI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.59659091\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607150934pJMSCw1yXdKx7Z4e.jpg\" title=\"维拉岛\" alt=\"维拉岛\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>维拉岛</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071509353j7CRmiQF6h8GxVc.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65520833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607150935OgUElP1aMfJmvs5n.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t        \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t图片来自<a href=\"http://www.gooood.hk/tavaru-in-velaa-private-island-by-adr-s-r-o.htm\" target=\"_blank\"> gooood</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}